quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,203,"Munasingize Allah mu minsi mbarwa 27. Ariko uzigira ubwira akahamara iminsi ibiri, nta cyaha kuri we, kandi n’uzatinda (kuva Mina) nta cyaha kuri we, kuri wawundi utinya Allah. Munatinye Allah kandi mumenye ko iwe ari ho muzakoranyirizwa"
  2,204,"No mu bantu, hari ugushimisha (yewe Muhamadi) kubera imvugo ye (ashaka indonke) z’ubuzima bw’isi, anatangaho Allah umuhamya mu biri mu mutima we, kandi nyamara ari we munyempaka wa cyane (umwanzi ukomeye w’ubuyisilamu)"
  2,205,"N’iyo ahindukiye (yewe Muhamadi avuye iwawe), azenguruka mu isi ayikoramo ubwangizi, akanangiza ibihingwa n’amatungo. Kandi Allah ntakunda ubwangizi"
  2,206,"N’iyo abwiwe ati \"Tinya Allah\", ubwibone bumugusha mu cyaha. Ubwo rero, Umuriro wa Jahanamu uramuhagije (kumukosora). Kandi mu byukuri,ni na yo saso mbi"
  2,207,"No mu bantu, hari abitanga bashaka ishimwe rya Allah, kandi Allah ni Nyiribambe ku bagaragu (be)"
  2,208,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwinjire mu buyisilamu byimazeyo (mwubahiriza amategeko n’amabwiriza byabwo), kandi ntimuzakurikire inzira za Shitani. Mu by’ukuri, ni umwanzi wanyu ugaragara"
  2,209,"Nimuteshuka (ku kuri) nyuma yo kugerwaho n’ibimenyetso bigaragara (bya Allah), mumenye ko mu by’ukuri, Allah ari Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ushishoza"
  2,210,"Ese hari ikindi bategereje kitari uko Allah abageraho n’Abamalayika mu gicucu cy’ibicu (ku munsi w’imperuka), maze urubanza (rwabo) rugacibwa? Kandi kwa Allah ni ho ibintu byose bizasubizwa"